name: Cook'n Cookbook Backup File
summary: Learn about .CK9 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: To create a CK9 backup file, select File → Backup and specify a backup location. To restore a backup file, select File → Restore.
NOTE: Use caution when restoring a backup file since all current cookbook data will be overwritten.

description: Backup file created by Cook'n, a program used to store cookbook recipes; contains a backup of a .DVO cookbook file; used for recovering lost data in the event that a DVO file is lost or corrupted.
